parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Airbag and Seat Belt System Failure
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag and seat belt system can lead to the airbag not deploying in the event of a crash, which can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light illuminates on the dashboard
the passenger airbag off light stays on
the seat belt warning light illuminates
the airbag sensor light illuminates
cracks appear on the dashboard around the airbag
and the airbag covering has cracked on either side of the passenger side front airbag module.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power seat can cause the seat to move unexpectedly, pinning the driver against the steering wheel, which can lead to accidents or loss of control of the vehicle.
symptoms: The seat moves independently
tilts forward
or reclines backward without input from the driver; the seat adjusts itself while driving; the seat belt tightens unexpectedly; the seat moves forward
pinning the driver against the steering wheel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS module can cause the vehicle to become unsafe to drive, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The ABS light comes on
the vehicle's braking system is affected
the battery is drained
the vehicle is unable to accelerate
and other electrical systems may malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electrical system can cause various systems to malfunction, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The check engine light comes on
the ESC off light comes on
the vehicle's acceleration is affected
the sunroof window
back driver window
and heated front seats may stop working
and the airbag lights may stay on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the power seat can cause the driver to be pinned to the steering wheel, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The driver's seat moves independently
reclines
moves forward and backward without any input
and may pin the driver to the steering wheel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag system can cause the airbags to deploy incorrectly or not deploy at all, leading to injuries or fatalities in the event of an accident.
symptoms: The airbag light comes on
the passenger airbag light stays on
the passenger seatbelt indicator light comes on
and the airbag system may malfunction.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The corrosion of the head gasket can cause oil to leak onto the alternator, leading to engine failure and potentially causing accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: Oil leaks onto the alternator
the engine light comes on
and the alternator may short out.
